*********Project Overview************

This project is a To-Do List application using Django for the frontend and FastAPI for the backend API.

Features:

Create, Read, Update, Delete tasks

Task fields: title, description, due_date, status

Beautiful, responsive frontend with modal forms

FastAPI Swagger documentation

***Setup & Installation

1. Clone the Repository

git clone https://github.com/om999-tech/todolist
cd <repo-folder>

2. Create a Virtual Environment

Linux / Mac:

python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate

***Windows (cmd):

python -m venv venv
.\venv\Scripts\Activate

3. Install Python Dependencies

pip install --upgrade pip
pip install -r requirements.txt

**Database Setup

1.Create the database

CREATE DATABASE todo_db;

2.Create tasks table:

CREATE TABLE tasks (
    id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    due_date DATE,
    status VARCHAR(50) DEFAULT 'pending'
);

3.Configure database connection

import mysql.connector

def get_connection():
    return mysql.connector.connect(
        host="localhost",
        user="root",
        password="your_password",
        database="todo_db"
    )

******Start FastAPI Server
uvicorn api.main:app --reload --port 4000 #(desire port or exclude port)

******Open in Browser:

Frontend: http://127.0.0.1:4000/
API Docs (Swagger): http://127.0.0.1:4000/api